第1回 地域医療とは[ The first time: What is Community Healthcare? ]
授業概要の説明と質疑応答を行った後、地域医療とはなにかについて講義を行う。具体的には、地域医療と隣接する概念である家庭医療、総合医について比較しながら説明を行うことで、地域医療の概念をより鮮明にする。また、地域医療の個別具体例を紹介しながら、問題に関連する原因が複雑に絡み合っていることを示し、問題の把握自体が難しいことを考える。

After having had an explanation of content of class study and a question-and-answer session, a lecture on what the community healthcare is. Specifically, the concept of the community healthcare will be made clearer by explanation of the home medical care that has an adjacent concept with the community healthcare and the comprehensive medical care while comparing between them. It is shown that the causes relating to the problem are connected complicatedly with each other while introducing the individual specific example of the community healthcare, and students think about that grasping of the problem itself is difficult
第2回 地域医療と保険制度[ Community Healthcare and Insurance System ]
日本の医療システムに関する基本的な説明を行う。具体的には、根拠となっている国民健康保険法と、保険制度の種類、財源調達の方法、支払い方式などについて説明する。 
※基本的な知識については、映像教材や配布資料に基づき予習すること。

Basic concept of medical care system in Japan will be explained. Specifically, the National Health Insurance Act as the basis of the medical care system, kind of the insurance regime, a method of resource procurement, and a payment method, etc. will be explained. ※About the basic knowledge, students should prepare for tomorrow's lesson based on the picture teaching materials and distributed documents.
第3回 地域医療の提供体制[ Community Healthcare Provisioning System ]
国が医療法で医療提供体制の種類や配置基準などの骨格を定めており、都道府県が保健医療計画で病床規制を中心とした具体的な内容を定めていることを説明する。さらに、地域ケア整備構想や介護保険事業支援計画、地域医療再生計画など、昨今新しく提供体制に関して整備されてきている計画についても概説した上で、4疾病（がん、脳卒中、急性心筋梗塞、糖尿病）5事業（救急、災害、へき地、周産期、小児）の提供体制について詳しく論じる 
※基本的な知識については、映像教材や配布資料に基づき予習すること。

It is explained that the government is establishing the frameworks such as a kind or the placement standard of the medical care provisioning system in Medical Service Act, and that the prefectural and city government are establishing the concrete contents mainly on the sickbed regulation in their respective healthcare planning. In addition, After having given an explanation of overview of plans that have been newly maintained recently about the provisioning system such as the community healthcare initiative, a provisioning scheme of four diseases (cancer, stroke, acute myocardial infarction, and diabetes) and five businesses (ambulance, disaster, isolated area, the perinatal period, and infant) will be discussed in detail.
第4回 地域医療を支える人材育成[ Personnel training to support a community medicine ]
医療を支える医師・看護師・保健師・理学療法士などの専門職種の育成状況を概観した後、へき地医療を中心とする医師を育成してきた自治医科大学の仕組み、最近広がりを見せている地域医療枠の入試制度の仕組みについて説明する。 
※基本的な知識については、映像教材や配布資料に基づき予習すること。

After having surveyed the upbringing situation of the specialized types of job such as a doctor, a nurse, a community health nurse, the physical therapist who are supporting the medical care, a structure of Jichi Medical University which has brought up doctors mainly on the medical care in isolated area, the structure of the entrance examination system of a community medicine frame that is showing a trend of expansion recently will be explained.
